KzGGdubVgEF5sS7L1-xOnc-pA&oe=6734A783"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "gymclass_trailer_cover_image_v05.png", "id": "794105814977946", "uri": "https://scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982516_794105818311279_4409523219033140330_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=rvOvdyJdypoQ7kNvgEyOIOa&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYC6lujvW1cic6hhuIsNYrb8Pv0ljrdz9O4y1KKMeZEzQQ&oe=67347FCB"}, "display_name": "GYM CLASS - BASKETBALL VR", "keywords": ["basketball", "nba", "sports", "social", "football"], "long_description": "**GYM CLASS is the top VR basketball & sports game \ud83c\udfc0\ud83c\udfc8\u26be** \n\nExperience NBA licensed team courts, full-court multiplayer games, massive worlds, simulation physics, and football & baseball stadiums. Rated best on Quest - make friends or level-up to be the best among millions in the top VR sports community.\n\n{8704248146300574}\n\n**Download GC FREE to experience:** \n- \u2795 Unparalleled Simulation Physics: The most realistic physics in gaming. Control your shots, passes, dribble moves, and dunks like never before.\n- \ud83c\udfae Multiplayer Games: Play half, fullcourt, and minigames with friends or AI.\n- \ud83c\udf0d Social Worlds: Connect with friends in massive environments.\n- \ud83c\udfc8\u26be Multi-Sport: Basketball, football, baseball, arcade, & more.\n- \ud83c\udfa8 Endless Styles: Complete Quests to unlock cosmetics - hoodies, shirts, jerseys, suits, glasses, hats, mascot costumes, green sounds, & more.\n- \ud83c\udfc6 Level-up & Stats: Track deep stats (shots, assists, rebounds)\n\n{2315442282123322}\n\n**Buy the NBA Bundle to get:**\n- \ud83d\ude2e NBA team courts: Hoop on virtual replicas of all 30 NBA team courts with friends or AI.\n- \ud83c\udfc6 NBA team branded apparel & challenges: Two different sets of team-branded apparel, a team-branded basketball, and team-branded hat. Play games to unlock further items.\n- \ud83d\udc55 NBA Bundle premium items: Additional NBA & team-branded shirts, hoodies, basketballs & accessories is available to purchase separately.\n\n{969686844967912}\n\n**GC PRO unlocks:**\n- \ud83c\udfe0 Private Courts: Customize your world, set your rules. Play with friends privately on a wide set of GC environments.\n- \ud83d\udc55 Full-body Avatars: Design your player w/ max control. Hairstyles, face details, facial hair, body shapes, height, tattoos, and more.\n- \ud83c\udfa8 Cosmetics: Unlock a wide variety of cosmetics from hoodies, glasses, headphones, & gorilla around w/ banana hats.\n- \ud83e\udd16 Design Your Bot: Name, design, and level-up your bot. \n\n{557813239965509}", "short_description": "\ud83c\udfc0\ud83c\udfc8\u26be GYM CLASS is the top VR basketball & sports game. Experience NBA licensed team courts, full-court multiplayer games, massive worlds, simulation physics, and football & baseball stadiums. Rated best on Quest - make friends or level-up to be the best among millions in the top VR sports community."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://gymclassvr.com/privacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://gymclassvr.com/tos", "publisher_name": "IRL Studios Inc.", "support_website_url": "https://gymclassvr.com/support", "website_url": "https://gymclassvr.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2776542286000603"}, {"id": "1023770785722696"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["SIMULATION", "SOCIAL", "SPORTS"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user